"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"8250ae",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"<50% scalp involvement: watchful waiting, topical glucocorticoids ± topical minoxidil, anthralin, intralesional glucocorticoid"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"6373f5",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
">50% scalp involvement: topical immunotherapy (squaric acid or DPCP); topical glucocorticoids for all patients; topical minoxidil, phototherapy, systemic immunosuppressants, wigs or other cosmetic camouflage, intralesional triamcinolone for brows, and bimatoprost for eyelashes may be used"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
